some packages you need:
ffmpeg 
tor, optionally
ffmpeg probably wants x264, libopus and some other stuff

imagemagick might need more RAM to convert pdfs: https://github.com/ImageMagick/ImageMagick/issues/396; also having policy issue with pdfs, see
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42928765/convertnot-authorized-aaaa-error-constitute-c-readimage-453

puppeteer has issues with snap installed chrome, try this if you get mount change issues:

  snap disconnect chromium:dot-local-share-applications
  snap disconnect chromium:dot-local-share-icons
 
